 # models

 ## Purpose
-Immutable data classes representing the application's domain model. These define the shape of fractal parameters, presets, view state, and export configuration.
+Immutable data classes representing the application's domain model. Root Dart files are compatibility facades; implementations live in responsibility subfolders.

-## Key Files
+## Subdirectories
+
+| Directory | Purpose |
+|-----------|---------|
+| `fractal/` | Fractal parameter schemas, render parameter snapshots, presets, and view state |
+| `palette/` | Color palette definitions and palette JSON serialization |
+| `export/` | Image and video export option models and export dimension policy |
+| `exploration/` | Exploration session statistics model |
+| `wallpaper/` | Wallpaper option models and platform target value types |
+
+## Root Facades

 | File | Description |
 |------|-------------|
-| `fractal_parameter.dart` | `FractalParameter` - defines a single configurable parameter (type, range, step, default) with `FractalParamType` enum |
-| `fractal_params.dart` | `FractalParams` - collection of parameter values as a typed map |
-| `fractal_preset.dart` | `FractalPreset` - named snapshot of parameters + view state + palette for save/restore |
-| `fractal_view_state.dart` | `FractalViewState` - pan offset, zoom level, rotation angles for the viewport |
-| `fractal_palette.dart` | `FractalPalette` - color palette definition for fractal coloring |
-| `export_options.dart` | `ExportOptions` - image export configuration (resolution, format, transparency) |
-| `video_export_options.dart` | `VideoExportOptions` - video/GIF export settings (duration, FPS, resolution) |
-| `exploration_stats.dart` | `ExplorationStats` - statistics tracking for exploration sessions |
-| `wallpaper_options.dart` | `WallpaperOptions` - wallpaper export settings (placement, scaling) |
+| `fractal_parameter.dart` | Re-exports `fractal/fractal_parameter.dart` |
+| `fractal_params.dart` | Re-exports `fractal/fractal_params.dart` |
+| `fractal_preset.dart` | Re-exports `fractal/fractal_preset.dart` |
+| `fractal_view_state.dart` | Re-exports `fractal/fractal_view_state.dart` |
+| `fractal_palette.dart` | Re-exports `palette/fractal_palette.dart` |
+| `export_options.dart` | Re-exports `export/export_options.dart` |
+| `video_export_options.dart` | Re-exports `export/video_export_options.dart` |
+| `exploration_stats.dart` | Re-exports `exploration/exploration_stats.dart` |
+| `wallpaper_options.dart` | Re-exports wallpaper options and target contracts |

 ## For AI Agents

